## Test Flow (on your phone)
1. Register as **Doctor** → set schedule & treatments
2. Dashboard shows live stats (initially 0)
3. **New Appointment** → create a call-by or walk-in
4. **View Appointments** → search by name, filter by status
5. **Available Slots** → navigate dates, see color-coded grid
6. **Settings** → join clinic with Clinic ID
7. Register as **Clinic** → "Add Doctor" shows shareable Clinic ID
